title: BRIEF-E*Trade Financial Daily Average Revenue Trades For Jan. Were 315,572, 29 Pct Increase From Dec
text:
13 PM / Updated 9 minutes ago BRIEF-E*Trade Financial Daily Average Revenue Trades For Jan. Were 315,572, 29 Pct Increase From Dec Reuters Staff 
Feb 12 (Reuters) - E*Trade Financial Corp: 
* E*TRADE FINANCIAL CORPORATION REPORTS MONTHLY ACTIVITY FOR JANUARY 2018 
* E*TRADE FINANCIAL CORP - DAILY AVERAGE REVENUE TRADES (DARTS) FOR JANUARY WERE 315,572, A 29 PERCENT INCREASE FROM DECEMBER 
* E*TRADE FINANCIAL CORP - NET NEW BROKERAGE ASSETS WERE $1.5 BILLION IN MONTH Source text for Eikon: Further company coverage:
